{"tid":1821591,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今次個兩隻00後真係笑死！","createTime":"2020-01-12T11:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T13:26:11.000Z","uid":36143,"like":11,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2a3cc619eb74cf5ab362deff60b6a0dc77373333","tid":1821591,"uid":36143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:52:48.000Z","msg":"話說小妹都放左段長假去散心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上個星期返到公司啲同事都好warm wellcum小妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知留意有兩個傻下傻下既00後做煙腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁當然即刻行去佢地背面嚇下佢地la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知聽到兩條00後係度睇睇緊扮工版連登，重開個excel打低啲headline<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁公司就規定唔可以係工作時間做私人野<br />\n<br />\n小妹咪即就刻一野拍佢地個頭再叫佢地入房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後大聲咁鬧個兩個傻仔，屈佢地交個account 出黎話check下有無洩漏公司機密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點知兩個傻仔又配合<br />\n<br />\n而家見到個傻仔mark曬成人台啲post，我一陣就cap曬send比all staf，睇佢地重點問post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你班00後等做我分身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c17c4fa040967a37080dfab5846b7358c45925","tid":1821591,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:59:32.000Z","msg":"老吉 請開命啦"},{"pid":"de7287e0023aaa8fff473fcb34309597276957b0","tid":1821591,"uid":105911,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:59:46.000Z","msg":"今次呢篇唔係好得，質素冇以前咁好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7aca727969dadce2809f67cf506ea9c13b3ae8f","tid":1821591,"uid":66365,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T12:05:27.000Z","msg":"90後已經過時